Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:15.85,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo, Hong Kong, Singapore...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:13.98,Jojo-HongKong,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,890)}Hong Kong
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.59,0:00:17.15,Jojo-Singapore,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1093)}Singapore
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:20.54,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,And now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.93,0:00:22.02,Jojo-Calcutta,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(90,1083)}Calcutta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:23.63,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,we're about to cross India...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:28.75,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,But, well, I'm a little worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:32.17,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,My image of India is a place where people
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:35.53,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,only eat curry and you \Ncould fall ill at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:39.63,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried that my body may not \Nbe able to handle the culture gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.57,0:00:42.64,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,That assessment is rather distorted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.01,0:00:46.95,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't worry. It's a nice \Ncountry, where simple people live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:49.15,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I can guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:55.28,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're in Calcutta. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:57.70,JoJo-Honk,SFX,0000,0000,0000,,Honk
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:00:59.33,JoJo-main,kid a,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, give me a tip!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:01.16,JoJo-main,adult a,0000,0000,0000,,Let me carry that for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:04.08,JoJo-main,adult b,0000,0000,0000,,Want a tattoo? You're so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.85,0:01:07.51,JoJo-main,adult c,0000,0000,0000,,Need some anti-venom? \NIt won't hurt your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.51,0:01:08.50,JoJo-main,adult d,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you a hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:11.08,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Calcutta, India.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:15.01,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,In the 20th century,\N its population is 11 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:18.76,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,An immense energy swirls about the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:22.50,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I stepped in some cow shit! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.50,JoJo-overlap,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:24.77,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,My wallet's already been stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:24.77,JoJo-overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, no thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.40,0:01:26.65,JoJo-main,kid,0000,0000,0000,,Tip! Tip! Tip!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:29.15,JoJo-main,kid,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't give me a tip,\N you won't go to heaven, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:32.03,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't put your nose on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:34.74,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,A-Avdol! Is this India?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.48,0:01:37.53,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,See? Isn't it a great country?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:41.23,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,This is what makes this country so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:58.47,JoJo-MainTitle,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(208,1)}JoJo's {\c&H2E0FB2&}Bizarre Adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:58.47,JoJo-MainTitle2,text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(208,1)}Stardust Crusaders
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:17.45,JoJo-EpTitle,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(461,462)}Episode 10: The Emperor and the Hanged Man Part 1
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:19.30,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Here, have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:25.50,JoJo-Location,blahblah,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,459)\b0\fs18}This story is fiction. The characters, groups, places, laws, and names \Nused in this program have no connection to any existing in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.24,JoJo-top,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,This is chai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:23.09,JoJo-top,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:24.04,JoJo-topinternal,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Chai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:26.01,JoJo-topinternal,nar,0000,0000,0000,,A popular drink in India.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:30.14,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,A sweet drink made by boiling\N black tea, sugar, and ginger with milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:32.90,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,At last, a little peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:34.66,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a matter of getting used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:38.37,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Once you get used to it,\Nyou'll see how wonderful this country is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:41.14,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,I like this place. It's pretty great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:44.28,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, Jotaro? You really mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:48.49,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about culture shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:51.16,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I'll like it once I get used to it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:56.09,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they say that people\N adapt to their surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:57.43,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the john?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:59.23,JoJo-main,boy a,0000,0000,0000,,It's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:00.99,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:01.87,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:03.68,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What about your order?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:04.64,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.85,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It had better be something amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:11.07,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Gorgeous, splendid food \Nthat suits a Frenchman like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:15.29,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Which means we can pick anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:18.03,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, something he'll like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:19.69,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:25.12,JoJo-main,boy b,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please wait, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:30.08,JoJo-main,boy b,0000,0000,0000,,Please use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:35.07,JoJo-main,polna,0000,0000,0000,,What's this stick for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:35.83,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.27,0:04:50.53,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,The toilet's shaped oddly, but it's pretty clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:55.43,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,A nice guy like myself can't\N stand it when bathrooms are dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:09.53,JoJo-main,boy b,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:13.51,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,D-D-D-D-Don't "Is something wrong?" at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:17.32,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-Th-Th-The toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.21,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,The toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:24.70,JoJo-Oink,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Oink
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:23.27,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,There's a pig sticking\N its head out of the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:29.04,JoJo-main,boy b,0000,0000,0000,,This toilet is unusual, even in India.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:32.87,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,They accidentally made the\N pig pen down below a little too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:36.08,JoJo-main,boy b,0000,0000,0000,,So when the pig gets hungry, \Nit sticks its head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:38.35,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not what I'm aski—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:43.03,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Er, wait, what?!\N That means this pig's food is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:46.81,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:49.87,JoJo-main,boy b,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.08,JoJo-main,boy b,0000,0000,0000,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:58.27,JoJo-main,boy b,0000,0000,0000,,See? Now you can go while the pig's \Nrecoiling from the blow to the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:03.16,JoJo-main,boy b,0000,0000,0000,,Our manager actually gets the\N pig to lick his butt and always says
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:06.42,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,how great it is, because he gets so clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:12.80,JoJo-main,boy b,0000,0000,0000,,Please, take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:15.42,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! Don't leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:17.77,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:24.76,JoJo-Menacing3,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Menacing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:23.00,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I could ever get used to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:29.16,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait until we get to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:32.52,JoJo-main,boy a,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:36.20,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:48.76,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:53.39,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I could have sworn I\N saw something weird there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:57.67,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I must have imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.60,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:02.10,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, there was a pig in the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:06.79,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It's not surprising I'd see an illusion \Nof a monster outside the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:11.17,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what they mean \Nby culture shock in India.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:23.00,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:23.88,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:25.82,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:31.34,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:34.55,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I can only see it in the mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:38.85,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the mirror Stand \Nthat Jotaro heard about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:41.10,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:44.10,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,This really isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:50.11,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Chariot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:57.70,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:07:59.67,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:04.12,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:07.13,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the user? Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:09.88,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,The man with two right hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:17.51,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:18.65,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:20.01,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Polnareff?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:21.18,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:23.02,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,If that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:27.41,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,If that was the Stand, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.48,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,That means he's finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:35.03,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro, the Stand user you heard \Nabout that uses mirrors is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:40.70,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,The bastard that killed my little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:50.29,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,The bastard that stepped all\N over my sister's life, soul, and pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:54.12,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally... I can finally see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:56.83,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The one you seek vengeance upon is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:03.21,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Joestar, I'll be traveling on my own here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:03.98,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Wh—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:08.79,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I know the guy\N who killed my sister is nearby,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:12.06,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to wait\N for him to come after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.59,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be at a disadvantage \Nif I let him attack me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:16.21,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's not my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:18.60,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find him first, and kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:21.54,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you don't know what \Nhe looks like, or what his Stand is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:24.50,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing that he has two right hands is plenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:28.19,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,And he knows that I'm after him, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:31.79,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,He should be worried that I'll \Ncome for his head in his sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:33.25,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:37.85,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,You'll go out for wool,\N only to come home shorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:39.68,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:42.16,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Just as it sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:45.35,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Are you implying that I'm going to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:46.10,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:51.45,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see that the enemy\N purposely attacked to get you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:54.01,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow you to travel alone, Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.28,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. I'm going to make this clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:10:00.50,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I never cared about DIO.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:04.43,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I told you in Hong Kong that \NI was only traveling with you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:05.83,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I could get my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:09.64,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Joestar and Jotaro \Nshould already know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.93,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I've been alone from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:14.76,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been fighting alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:15.96,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Such a selfish man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:18.82,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget that you \Nwere brainwashed by DIO?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:21.95,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten that \Nthis all leads back to DIO?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:25.98,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Like you'd ever understand how \NI feel after having my sister killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:30.48,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that the last time you met DIO,\N you got scared and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:35.46,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,A coward like you would \Nnever understand how I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:36.49,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.10,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:41.04,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You were just lucky that \Nyou beat me in Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:42.70,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lecture me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:43.99,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:46.41,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did that piss you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:51.75,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,But don't forget that I'm a lot more\N pissed off than you are right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:57.37,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You can just keep acting like\N the mature one as always, Avdol.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:59.13,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.87,0:11:01.05,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:03.93,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough. Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:07.78,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Now that he's like this, no one can stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:13.31,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm just disappointed in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:16.16,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think he was that sort of man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:21.09,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I did indeed run in fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:24.45,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,That's also why I believe we will win,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:26.98,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and can say with certainty that you'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:28.12,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:31.28,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll say this with certainty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:35.30,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Your divination will be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:54.69,JoJo-Oink,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Tromp Tromp Tromp
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:03.97,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.71,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to see a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:11.71,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Go back yourself from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:16.50,JoJo-main,nena,0000,0000,0000,,Please, make me your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:21.45,JoJo-main,nena,0000,0000,0000,,I will dedicate my life to you.\NJust tell me whatever you wish of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:26.26,JoJo-main,nena,0000,0000,0000,,So please, let me stay by your side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:30.27,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid. You're still only sixteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.02,JoJo-main,nena,0000,0000,0000,,I'm old enough to marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:34.88,JoJo-main,nena,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:47.22,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. I'm just a drifter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:52.19,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,I live each day like it's my last, \Nand one day, it will be my last.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.84,0:12:59.27,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Royalty like yourself can't\N think about marrying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:02.70,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much we love each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:03.59,JoJo-main,nena,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:06.59,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:10.10,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You're the only one \NI love in the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:13.72,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:17.97,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I love you that I can't marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:19.37,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:25.58,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard for me, too.\N My chest feels like it could burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:32.52,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll come see you once in \Na while and hold you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:35.28,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough to make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:37.21,JoJo-main,nena,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:45.05,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Later. Love ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:14:00.39,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,It's not nice to eavesdrop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:06.06,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'd like to say\N I'm being as indirect as ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.06,0:14:08.57,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,and that there're girls like her everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:11.44,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,But she's an easy mark, and it's convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:15.38,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,She'd do anything for me,\N even throw away her own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:19.58,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,You know how I work, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:23.58,JoJo-Menacing4,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Menacing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:21.98,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Centerfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:30.62,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, about Silver Chariot's Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:33.39,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Seems he's looking for you on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:35.20,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:39.73,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,He fell hook, line, and sinker \Nfor your plan to lure him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:42.49,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we kill him first?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:58.54,JoJo-Blam,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Blam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:17.16,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:23.52,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,With you and your Hanged Man,\N and me, Hol Horse, with my Emperor,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.93,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,We can kill 'em all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:00.98,JoJo-Eyecatch3,sign top,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(793,1)}Hanged Man
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:00.98,JoJo-Eyecatch2,sign bot,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(877,1)}Centerfold
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:10.63,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,So he didn't come back after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:36.30,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:37.81,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You saw him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:41.24,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure you saw a\N man with two right hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:43.64,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.82,JoJo-main,man,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:02.58,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost him. He was just right there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:03.98,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:07.29,JoJo-main,man,0000,0000,0000,,He was with that man right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:09.17,JoJo-Fwish,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Fwoosh
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:14.67,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,The gun is mightier than the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:18.48,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Man, talk about a memorable quote.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:21.77,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:26.19,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Hol Horse is the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:30.98,JoJo-main,jol,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the user of the Stand \Nthat suggests the Emperor card.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:36.75,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Lord DIO paid me to get rid of you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:40.16,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, country boy.\NI don't need the self-introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:43.43,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the man with two right hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:47.01,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was rude.\N You asked, so I answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:49.17,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:51.17,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,I came here with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.01,0:17:53.44,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,He's nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:54.26,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:55.65,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:58.22,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,No point in asking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:02.52,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,I, Hol Horse, will be taking care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:06.29,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Trash like you always says that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:08.73,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,and it always ends up the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:11.59,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Was that funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:17.64,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Lord DIO said that Polnareff was \Na man who underestimated others,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:20.24,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,and that I'd have no problem beating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:24.39,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,He was exactly right,\N so I couldn't help but laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:30.76,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't see him until I defeat you, \Nthen that's just what I'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:32.88,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:35.82,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,You know Stratego, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:39.71,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,The tank is stronger than the soldier, \Nand tanks are weak against mines.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:42.33,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,See, it's pretty much the basics of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:46.63,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,My Emperor is stronger than you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:50.65,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I'd let you know about\N my Stand's abilities before we fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:53.46,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,The gun is mightier than the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:56.15,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, such a memorable quote.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:18:59.41,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:02.32,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,My Stand shoots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.33,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,A sword can't beat a weapon that shoots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:06.60,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,So, what? A pea shooter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.41,JoJo-main,both,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:23.16,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,You underestimated me, Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:23.26,JoJo-Blam,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,218)}Blam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:26.10,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,And now, you've lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:29.00,JoJo-Fwoom,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Fwoom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:31.10,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,If it takes off its armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:33.93,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing but a bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:37.15,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:39.85,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible! The trajectory curved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:41.16,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,C-Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:44.07,JoJo-internal/narrator,hol,0000,0000,0000,,The bullet is also my Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:47.05,JoJo-internal/narrator,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Underestimating me by \Nnot even considering that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:49.16,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,will cost you your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:54.48,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:02.13,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Wha— Avdol!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:05.35,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I went looking for you because \NI was worried, and look what I find!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:07.44,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,You're too full of yourself, Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:09.06,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,W-Worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:11.89,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Are you going to lecture me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:14.56,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy knows everything about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:16.44,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,You said you've lived life alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.67,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,but from now on,\N you won't be able to win alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:22.45,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,What bad timing for an outsider to interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.74,JoJo-Curve,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1147,1)}Curve
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.13,0:20:27.57,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Move, Polnareff! The bullet's coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:30.13,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Magician's Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:33.37,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I'll burn it to cinders!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:41.26,JoJo-internal/narrator,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Avdol!\N He went after Polnareff himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:48.01,JoJo-internal/narrator,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Mr. Avdol? Polnareff?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:50.35,JoJo-internal/narrator,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,I have a terrible feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:52.89,JoJo-main,voice,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's a weird fight going on over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:08.33,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,The puddle...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:14.83,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:31.01,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Avdol!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:34.92,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Man, today must be my day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:40.00,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,My gun and Centerfold's mirror\N don't do very well with Avdol's flames,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:42.62,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,so we thought he'd be \Nour most formidable enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.62,0:21:43.99,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:48.31,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,There are no scary pieces\N left in this game of Stratego.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:50.76,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Avdol!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.92,0:21:57.88,JoJo-internal/narrator,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's just hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:21:59.55,JoJo-internal/narrator,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a minor wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:01.38,JoJo-internal/narrator,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,See? He's going to start speaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:03.41,JoJo-internal/narrator,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,He'll open his eyes at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.06,0:22:06.06,JoJo-internal/narrator,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Mr. Avdol?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:08.84,JoJo-internal/narrator,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to wake up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:11.14,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Avdol, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.42,0:22:13.59,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Mr. Avdol!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.53,0:22:26.00,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible. This was too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:28.91,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was too quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:36.46,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he gets for lecturing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.46,0:22:37.85,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Look at him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:38.42,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:40.62,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say, Polnareff?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.14,0:22:43.17,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Avdol was worried about you—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:46.17,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Who asked him for help?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.74,0:22:49.06,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,He likes to meddle in other people's business,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:51.30,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's slow as hell, so they got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:54.31,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Guys like him just get in the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.31,0:22:56.94,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I said I'd do this myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:22:58.79,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.33,0:23:02.33,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,He saved your life. How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.33,0:23:15.16,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It really annoys me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.45,0:23:21.71,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Having people up and die on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.27,0:23:23.37,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Polnareff...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.40,0:23:31.22,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It just annoys me so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:37.01,JoJo-Preview,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.76,0:23:39.07,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a bold face, \Nand yet he died so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.07,0:23:41.77,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, she \Nwas really good at sobbing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:43.42,JoJo-main,hol,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.42,0:23:44.98,JoJo-main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to hold back?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:23:47.26,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fall for the enemy's provocation!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.26,0:23:49.99,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Avdol told you not to fight by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:49.99,JoJo-NextTitle,ep,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 11
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:49.99,JoJo-NextTitle2,sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Emperor and the Hanged Man Part 2
